Scrapbook includes press clippings and printed ephemera on the opening of Kootz Gallery and various exhibitions including one-man shows of: Fernand Leger; Alexander Calder; Romare Bearden; Carl Holty; Robert Motherwell; Byron Browne; and William Baziotes.
Tucked in the back of the scrapbook (loose) are issues of periodicals (Creative Design, Winter 1935-6; Art News, October 15-31, 1945 (cover only); Magazine of Art, Dec. 1945); and more press clippings, including reviews of Kootz's play Home is the Hunter.
Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution
